Package: p.post
Title: Calculate the Posterior Probability of Success
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("John", "Reeves", , "john.a.reeves@verizon.net", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Produces output (excel sheet, graphs) on P(p_post>x)>=y for a range of 
    x and y.  Prior is assumed to be Beta (1,1).
